Q.5\bullet  What do you understand by CSS opacity? \par
\par
answer=>  The opacity property sets the opacity level for an element.\par
\par
          The opacity-level describes the transparency-level,\par
           where 1 is not transparent at all, 0.5 is 50% see-through,\par
           and 0 is completely transparent.\par
