Q.8 \bullet  What is the use of the background-position property? \par
\par
answer=>  The background-position property sets the starting position of a background image.\par
\par
          Tip: By default, a background-image is placed at the top-left corner of an element, and repeated both vertically and horizontally.\par
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------/\par
